ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectAMBER DURUM WHEAT - 2008-2009 UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2010-2011 Pool **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the AMBER DURUM WHEAT unsold from the preceding pool that began on August 1, 2009, and ended on July 31, 2010, to the current pool period that began on August 1, 2010, and will end on July 31, 2011.
